[{"author_name":"Collette McDonald","author_url":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/109429403165924285101/reviews","language":"en","original_language":"en","profile_photo_url":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXTayX5cXeNGR8544uQHnh2D7SdcSlq00sXL594OAuGvLHKUByyJQ=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5","rating":5,"relative_time_description":"vor 5 Monaten","text":"Wir hatten das Brühe-Fondue und LIEBTEN den Salat und das Gemüse. Fleisch ist Fleisch, das in Brühe gekocht wird, also war es nicht allzu aufregend. Ich würde etwas anderes und weniger Touristenhaftes ausprobieren. Das „Französische“ Dressing war fantastisch! Es erinnerte uns Amerikaner an ein vereinfachtes Ranch-Dressing, aber definitiv kein Ranch-Dressing!

Die Anlage ist neuer als alles andere, was wir auf dieser Reise ausprobiert haben. Erinnert an ein Hotel im „Tagungs“-Zentrum-Stil in den Staaten. Das Personal war reizend und die Nussmischung an der Bar muss man probieren!","time":1736842377,"translated":false},{"author_name":"Sabine Vuskane","author_url":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/102814169623855795164/reviews","language":"en","original_language":"en","profile_photo_url":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXYydQGk0R57_0xWCZHuW_6znxFMLPonu-fQIZVzs7PL2PjASaT=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo","rating":5,"relative_time_description":"vor einem Monat","text":"Das Essen ist einfach großartig. Hatte Rinderbrühe mit Pfannkuchen, Rindfleisch auf heißen Steinen, das man selbst backen muss, Brokkoli. Die Atmosphäre ist schön, die Aussicht großartig, die Kellner professionell.","time":1747596736,"translated":false},{"author_name":"Doroteja Miksa","author_url":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/101421634062575998702/reviews","language":"en","original_language":"en","profile_photo_url":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVfV-_6Eu0aX9mYQFQRVAUknR9Oc5lPxUyTFTVGvy_PFMcprqNj=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3","rating":4,"relative_time_description":"vor einem Jahr","text":"War zweimal dort, beim ersten Mal lief alles gut, das Essen war lecker, Eierschwammerlgulasch ist ein Muss :)
Allerdings gab es beim zweiten Mal einige Enttäuschungen - das Nudelgericht wurde fast kalt serviert, die Ramen-Suppe war extrem salzig, kaum essbar und im Geschmackstiefgang nicht wirklich mit einem echten Ramen vergleichbar. Zum Nachtisch gab es die Wahl eines abgepackten Bechers Eiscreme, der leider alt und nicht gut war, also haben wir ihn zurückgegeben. Der Service ist extrem nett und freundlich, angenehme Atmosphäre. Insgesamt könnten einige Kleinigkeiten verbessert werden, aber wir werden sicherlich für einen weiteren Versuch zurückkehren.","time":1702802723,"translated":false},{"author_name":"Anouk Janine Braune","author_url":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/111569439928920748527/reviews","language":"en","original_language":"en","profile_photo_url":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWw-xqTl8DZiDEzhqHn6d8NwrbgwPd4RYWImTJJfYWYOH0QrwMl=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4","rating":4,"relative_time_description":"vor einem Jahr","text":"Das Restaurant hat ein sehr gemütliches Innendesign und wir hatten das Glück, an einem ruhigen Mittwochabend dort zu essen.

Wir bestellten Edamame, Caesar-Salat, Schnitzel und Ramen-Suppe.
Alles war sehr lecker, nur die Portion der Ramen-Suppe war nicht ausreichend für ein Hauptgericht. Und die Kartoffeln zum Schnitzel waren etwas geschmacklos.

Unser Kellner war sehr aufmerksam und freundlich.

Ein guter Abend und ein großartiger Ort für ein Abendessen mit köstlichem Essen!","time":1711193544,"translated":false},{"author_name":"Mattia Sighel","author_url":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/111194389316493434716/reviews","language":"en","original_language":"en","profile_photo_url":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUj540lGebo7vCM4h0BlZ7CA2M6vLAexzqelaVNI_tU_6Vq-qA=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo","rating":5,"relative_time_description":"vor einem Jahr","text":"Ein sehr angenehmes Mittagessen an einem großartigen Ort.
Das Essen war wirklich gut und seinen Preis wert, die Atmosphäre war sehr eindrucksvoll, besonders dank des großartigen Blicks durch die großen Fenster auf die Landschaft.","time":1702202414,"translated":false}]

[{"author_name":"Collette McDonald","author_url":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/109429403165924285101/reviews","language":"en","original_language":"en","profile_photo_url":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXTayX5cXeNGR8544uQHnh2D7SdcSlq00sXL594OAuGvLHKUByyJQ=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5","rating":5,"relative_time_description":"5 months ago","text":"We had the broth fondue and LOVED the salad and veggies.  Meat is meat cooked in broth so it was not too exciting. I would try something else and less touristy. The “French” dressing was fantastic! It reminded us Americans of a simplified ranch dressing, but definitely not ranch dressing!

The facility is newer than everything else we have tried on this trip. Reminiscent of a “convention” center type hotel in the states.  Staff was lovely and the nut mix at the bar is a must try!","time":1736842377,"translated":false},{"author_name":"Sabine Vuskane","author_url":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/102814169623855795164/reviews","language":"en","original_language":"en","profile_photo_url":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXYydQGk0R57_0xWCZHuW_6znxFMLPonu-fQIZVzs7PL2PjASaT=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo","rating":5,"relative_time_description":"a month ago","text":"The food is just great. Had beef broth with pancakes, beef on hot stones you have to bake yourself, brokoli. The atmosphere is nice, the views great, waiters professional.","time":1747596736,"translated":false},{"author_name":"Doroteja Miksa","author_url":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/101421634062575998702/reviews","language":"en","original_language":"en","profile_photo_url":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVfV-_6Eu0aX9mYQFQRVAUknR9Oc5lPxUyTFTVGvy_PFMcprqNj=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3","rating":4,"relative_time_description":"a year ago","text":"Went there 2 times, first time everything went well, food was delicious, eierschwammerl goulash is a must try :)
However second time there were a few let downs - pasta dish was served almost cold, ramen soup was extremely salty, couldn’t hardly eat it and can’t really compare to an actual ramen in depth of flavor. For dessert there was a choice of packaged cup of ice cream which, unfortunately, was old and not good so we returned it back. Service is extremely nice and friendly, pleasant atmosphere. Overall, a little bits and pieces could be improved but we’ll certainly come back again for another try.","time":1702802723,"translated":false},{"author_name":"Anouk Janine Braune","author_url":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/111569439928920748527/reviews","language":"en","original_language":"en","profile_photo_url":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWw-xqTl8DZiDEzhqHn6d8NwrbgwPd4RYWImTJJfYWYOH0QrwMl=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4","rating":4,"relative_time_description":"a year ago","text":"The restaurant has a very cozy interior design and we were lucky to eat on a quiet Wednesday evening.

We ordered Edamame, Caesar salad, Schnitzel and Ramen soup.
Everything was very delicious, just the portion of the Ramen soup was not enough for a main course. And the potatoes to the Schnitzel were a little tasteless.

Our waiter was very attentive and friendly.

A good evening and great place for a dinner with delicious food!","time":1711193544,"translated":false},{"author_name":"Mattia Sighel","author_url":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/111194389316493434716/reviews","language":"en","original_language":"en","profile_photo_url":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUj540lGebo7vCM4h0BlZ7CA2M6vLAexzqelaVNI_tU_6Vq-qA=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo","rating":5,"relative_time_description":"a year ago","text":"Very pleasant lunch in an awesome place.
The food was really good and worth the price, the atmosphere was really suggestive and especially thanks to the great view from the big windows of the landscape.","time":1702202414,"translated":false}]

[{"author_name":"Collette McDonald","author_url":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/109429403165924285101/reviews","language":"it","original_language":"en","profile_photo_url":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXTayX5cXeNGR8544uQHnh2D7SdcSlq00sXL594OAuGvLHKUByyJQ=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5","rating":5,"relative_time_description":"5 mesi fa","text":"Abbiamo provato la fonduta di brodo e abbiamo AMATO l'insalata e le verdure. La carne è carne cotta nel brodo, quindi non era troppo eccitante. Proverei qualcosa di diverso e meno turistico. Il condimento "francese" era fantastico! Ha ricordato a noi americani un condimento ranch semplificato, ma decisamente non un condimento ranch!

La struttura è più nuova di tutto il resto che abbiamo provato in questo viaggio. Ricorda un tipo di hotel da “convegno” negli Stati Uniti. Il personale era adorabile e il mix di noci al bar è assolutamente da provare!","time":1736842377,"translated":false},{"author_name":"Sabine Vuskane","author_url":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/102814169623855795164/reviews","language":"it","original_language":"en","profile_photo_url":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXYydQGk0R57_0xWCZHuW_6znxFMLPonu-fQIZVzs7PL2PjASaT=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo","rating":5,"relative_time_description":"un mese fa","text":"Il cibo è semplicemente ottimo. Ho avuto brodo di manzo con frittelle, manzo su pietre calde che devi cuocere da te, broccoli. L'atmosfera è piacevole, le viste ottime, i camerieri professionali.","time":1747596736,"translated":false},{"author_name":"Doroteja Miksa","author_url":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/101421634062575998702/reviews","language":"it","original_language":"en","profile_photo_url":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVfV-_6Eu0aX9mYQFQRVAUknR9Oc5lPxUyTFTVGvy_PFMcprqNj=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3","rating":4,"relative_time_description":"un anno fa","text":"Sono andato lì 2 volte, la prima volta tutto è andato bene, il cibo era delizioso, il gulash di eierschwammerl è assolutamente da provare :)
Tuttavia, la seconda volta ci sono stati alcuni punti negativi: il piatto di pasta è stato servito quasi freddo, la zuppa di ramen era estremamente salata, a malapena l'ho mangiata e non può realmente essere paragonata a un vero ramen in termini di profondità del sapore. Per dessert c'era una scelta di coppa di gelato confezionata che, purtroppo, era vecchia e non buona, quindi l'abbiamo restituita. Il servizio è estremamente gentile e amichevole, atmosfera piacevole. Nel complesso, qualche piccola cosa potrebbe essere migliorata ma torneremo sicuramente per un altro tentativo.","time":1702802723,"translated":false},{"author_name":"Anouk Janine Braune","author_url":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/111569439928920748527/reviews","language":"it","original_language":"en","profile_photo_url":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWw-xqTl8DZiDEzhqHn6d8NwrbgwPd4RYWImTJJfYWYOH0QrwMl=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4","rating":4,"relative_time_description":"un anno fa","text":"Il ristorante ha un design d'interni molto accogliente e siamo stati fortunati a mangiare in un tranquillo mercoledì sera.

Abbiamo ordinato edamame, insalata Caesar, schnitzel e zuppa di ramen.
Tutto era molto delizioso, solo la porzione di zuppa di ramen non era sufficiente per un piatto principale. E le patate dello schnitzel erano un po' insipide.

Il nostro cameriere era molto attento e amichevole.

Una buona serata e un ottimo posto per una cena con cibo delizioso!","time":1711193544,"translated":false},{"author_name":"Mattia Sighel","author_url":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/111194389316493434716/reviews","language":"it","original_language":"en","profile_photo_url":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUj540lGebo7vCM4h0BlZ7CA2M6vLAexzqelaVNI_tU_6Vq-qA=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo","rating":5,"relative_time_description":"un anno fa","text":"Pranzo molto piacevole in un posto fantastico.
Il cibo era davvero buono e valeva il prezzo, l'atmosfera era davvero suggestiva, grazie soprattutto alla splendida vista dalle grandi finestre sul paesaggio.","time":1702202414,"translated":false}]

[{"author_name":"Collette McDonald","author_url":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/109429403165924285101/reviews","language":"fr","original_language":"en","profile_photo_url":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXTayX5cXeNGR8544uQHnh2D7SdcSlq00sXL594OAuGvLHKUByyJQ=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5","rating":5,"relative_time_description":"il y a 5 mois","text":"Nous avons pris la fondue au bouillon et ADORÉ la salade et les légumes. La viande est de la viande cuite dans le bouillon, donc ce n'était pas trop excitant. J'essaierais quelque chose d'autre et de moins touristique. La vinaigrette dite 'française' était fantastique ! Elle nous a rappelé, à nous Américains, une version simplifiée de la sauce ranch, sans être de la sauce ranch !

L'installation est plus récente que tout ce que nous avons essayé lors de ce voyage. Elle rappelle un hôtel de type centre 'de convention' aux États-Unis. Le personnel était adorable et le mélange de noix au bar est à essayer absolument !","time":1736842377,"translated":true},{"author_name":"Sabine Vuskane","author_url":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/102814169623855795164/reviews","language":"fr","original_language":"en","profile_photo_url":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXYydQGk0R57_0xWCZHuW_6znxFMLPonu-fQIZVzs7PL2PjASaT=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo","rating":5,"relative_time_description":"il y a un mois","text":"La nourriture est tout simplement excellente. J'ai eu un bouillon de bœuf avec des crêpes, du bœuf sur pierres chaudes que vous devez cuisiner vous-même, du brocoli. L'atmosphère est agréable, les vues superbes, les serveurs professionnels.","time":1747596736,"translated":true},{"author_name":"Doroteja Miksa","author_url":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/101421634062575998702/reviews","language":"fr","original_language":"en","profile_photo_url":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVfV-_6Eu0aX9mYQFQRVAUknR9Oc5lPxUyTFTVGvy_PFMcprqNj=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3","rating":4,"relative_time_description":"il y a un an","text":"Je suis allé là-bas deux fois, la première fois tout s'est bien passé, la nourriture était délicieuse, le goulash aux girolles est à essayer absolument :)
Cependant, la deuxième fois, il y a eu quelques déceptions - le plat de pâtes a été servi presque froid, la soupe ramen était extrêmement salée, j'ai à peine pu la manger et elle ne pouvait vraiment pas être comparée à un véritable ramen en termes de profondeur de saveur. Pour le dessert, il y avait un choix de coupe de glace emballée qui, malheureusement, était vieille et pas bonne donc nous l'avons retournée. Le service est extrêmement gentil et amical, l'atmosphère agréable. Dans l'ensemble, quelques petits détails pourraient être améliorés, mais nous reviendrons certainement pour un nouvel essai.","time":1702802723,"translated":true},{"author_name":"Anouk Janine Braune","author_url":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/111569439928920748527/reviews","language":"fr","original_language":"en","profile_photo_url":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWw-xqTl8DZiDEzhqHn6d8NwrbgwPd4RYWImTJJfYWYOH0QrwMl=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4","rating":4,"relative_time_description":"il y a un an","text":"Le restaurant a un intérieur très cosy et nous avons eu la chance de manger un mercredi soir tranquille.

Nous avons commandé des edamame, une salade César, un schnitzel et une soupe ramen. Tout était très délicieux, seule la portion de la soupe ramen n'était pas suffisante pour un plat principal. Et les pommes de terre accompagnant le schnitzel manquaient un peu de goût.

Notre serveur était très attentif et sympathique.

Une bonne soirée et un excellent endroit pour un dîner avec une nourriture délicieuse !","time":1711193544,"translated":true},{"author_name":"Mattia Sighel","author_url":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/111194389316493434716/reviews","language":"fr","original_language":"en","profile_photo_url":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUj540lGebo7vCM4h0BlZ7CA2M6vLAexzqelaVNI_tU_6Vq-qA=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo","rating":5,"relative_time_description":"il y a un an","text":"Déjeuner très agréable dans un endroit magnifique.
La nourriture était vraiment bonne et valait le prix, l'atmosphère était vraiment suggestive et surtout grâce à la superbe vue depuis les grandes fenêtres sur le paysage.","time":1702202414,"translated":true}]

[{"author_name":"Collette McDonald","author_url":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/109429403165924285101/reviews","language":"hr","original_language":"en","profile_photo_url":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXTayX5cXeNGR8544uQHnh2D7SdcSlq00sXL594OAuGvLHKUByyJQ=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5","rating":5,"relative_time_description":"prije 5 mjeseci","text":"Imali smo fondue s bujonom i obožavali salatu i povrće. Meso je meso kuhano u bujonu, tako da nije bilo previše uzbudljivo. Isprobala bih nešto drugo i manje turističko. Francuski umak je bio fantastičan! Podsjetilo nas Amerikance na pojednostavljeni ranch dressing, ali definitivno nije bio ranch dressing!

Objekt je noviji od svega ostalog što smo isprobali na ovom putovanju. Podsjeća na hotel tipa konferencijskog centra u SAD-u. Osoblje je bilo divno, a mješavina orašastih plodova u baru je obavezna za probati!","time":1736842377,"translated":true},{"author_name":"Sabine Vuskane","author_url":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/102814169623855795164/reviews","language":"hr","original_language":"en","profile_photo_url":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXYydQGk0R57_0xWCZHuW_6znxFMLPonu-fQIZVzs7PL2PjASaT=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo","rating":5,"relative_time_description":"prije mjesec dana","text":"Hrana je jednostavno odlična. Imali smo goveđu juhu s palačinkama, govedinu na vrućem kamenu koju sami morate ispeći, brokulu. Atmosfera je lijepa, pogledi su odlični, konobari profesionalni.","time":1747596736,"translated":true},{"author_name":"Doroteja Miksa","author_url":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/101421634062575998702/reviews","language":"hr","original_language":"en","profile_photo_url":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVfV-_6Eu0aX9mYQFQRVAUknR9Oc5lPxUyTFTVGvy_PFMcprqNj=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3","rating":4,"relative_time_description":"prije godinu dana","text":"Posjetili smo dvaput, prvi put je sve prošlo dobro, hrana je bila ukusna, eierschwammerl gulaš obavezno probajte :)
Međutim, drugi put bilo je nekoliko razočaranja - tjestenina je poslužena gotovo hladna, ramen juha je bila izrazito slana, jedva se mogla jesti i ne može se uspoređivati s pravim ramenom po dubini okusa. Za desert je ponuđena pakirana čaša sladoleda koja, nažalost, bila je stara i nije bila dobra pa smo je vratili. Usluga je iznimno ljubazna i prijateljska, ugodna atmosfera. Sveukupno, nekoliko sitnih detalja moglo bi se poboljšati, ali sigurno ćemo se vratiti ponovno za još jedno isprobavanje.","time":1702802723,"translated":true},{"author_name":"Anouk Janine Braune","author_url":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/111569439928920748527/reviews","language":"hr","original_language":"en","profile_photo_url":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWw-xqTl8DZiDEzhqHn6d8NwrbgwPd4RYWImTJJfYWYOH0QrwMl=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4","rating":4,"relative_time_description":"prije godinu dana","text":"Restoran ima vrlo ugodan unutarnji dizajn i imali smo sreću što smo jeli u mirnoj srijedu navečer.

Naručili smo Edamame, Caesar salatu, šniclu i ramen juhu.
Sve je bilo vrlo ukusno, jedino porcija ramen juhe nije bila dovoljna za glavno jelo. A krumpiri uz šniclu su bili malo bezokusa.

Naš konobar je bio vrlo pažljiv i ljubazan.

Dobra večer i odlično mjesto za večeru s ukusnom hranom!","time":1711193544,"translated":true},{"author_name":"Mattia Sighel","author_url":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/111194389316493434716/reviews","language":"hr","original_language":"en","profile_photo_url":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUj540lGebo7vCM4h0BlZ7CA2M6vLAexzqelaVNI_tU_6Vq-qA=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo","rating":5,"relative_time_description":"prije godinu dana","text":"Veoma ugodan ručak na prekrasnom mjestu.
Hrana je bila stvarno dobra i vrijedna cijene, atmosfera je bila stvarno sugestivna, posebno zahvaljujući prekrasnom pogledu kroz velike prozore na krajolik.","time":1702202414,"translated":true}]

[{"author_name":"javier montesquieu","author_url":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/107077685752724958204/reviews","language":"de","original_language":"en","profile_photo_url":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK2sFWZRCf-2RB-aeJpNmLpStbwAMSqr5EAm6JOzdfraOjcrg=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5","rating":1,"relative_time_description":"vor 4 Monaten","text":"Ich habe nach einem Zimmer mit Bergblick gefragt, und sie haben mir ein dunkles Zimmer mit Blick auf ein anderes Gebäude, etwa 3 m entfernt, gegeben. Die sehr junge und nicht sehr nette Dame an der Rezeption sagte mir bei der Reservierung, dass mein Zimmer zum Parkplatz, aber auch zu den Bergen ausgerichtet sei; nicht wahr. Sie sagte auch, dass es keine weiteren Zimmer verfügbar wären. Als ich dem Besitzer am nächsten Morgen sagte, dass ich gehen würde, sagte sie mir, sie würde mir ein anderes Zimmer besorgen... oh, jetzt wo ich gehe, sind plötzlich Zimmer verfügbar?? Ebenso war der Speisesaal schlecht beleuchtet, traurig, und der Service war miserabel: kein einziges Hallo, kein Lächeln... das Salatbuffet war auf Rentnerniveau, obwohl das Frühstück ziemlich gut war. Der Whirlpool war kaputt und die Tür zum Spa wurde nach 19 Uhr geschlossen (aber sie "wussten es nicht"), obwohl sie behaupten, es wäre bis viel später geöffnet. Dies ist kein 4-Sterne-Hotel.
